# Pulse Labs — Design System Rules

> **Always follow these rules when generating any UI code for this project.**

---

## 1. App Context

**App:** Pulse Knowledge — Personal AI Knowledge Base manager  
**Stack:** Next.js 16 (App Router), TypeScript, TailwindCSS v4, Lucide React icons  
**Theme:** Dark-only. No light mode. Full-app dark background.  
**Language:** Vietnamese UI (all user-facing text must be in Vietnamese).

---

## 2. Color System — ALWAYS USE THESE TOKENS

The SINGLE source of truth is `src/app/globals.css` (`@theme inline` block).

### Primary Green (Brand Identity)

The **entire app uses jade-emerald green** as its primary identity color. This is non-negotiable.

```css
/* Core green tokens — use these for ALL CTAs, focus states, active states, links */
--color-auth-accent:       oklch(0.75 0.19 160)   /* Primary CTA / active */
--color-auth-accent-dim:   oklch(0.75 0.19 160 / 0.12) /* Subtle bg on dark surface */
--color-auth-accent-dark:  oklch(0.65 0.19 160)   /* Hover state */
--color-auth-accent-glow:  oklch(0.75 0.19 160 / 0.35) /* Glow/shadow on hover */
```

### Tailwind Token Aliases

In Tailwind classes, these map as:
- **Primary CTA button**: `bg-auth-accent hover:bg-auth-accent-dark text-black font-semibold`
- **CTA gradient button**: `bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-500`
- **Active nav link**: `bg-auth-accent-dim text-auth-accent border border-auth-accent/20`
- **Focus ring**: `focus:border-auth-accent` (auto-applied via globals.css)
- **Text accent**: `text-auth-accent`
- **Icon dim bg**: `bg-auth-accent-dim text-auth-accent`

### Dark Surfaces (app-wide)

```
bg-auth-bg        → oklch(0.12 0.006 260) — page background
bg-auth-surface   → oklch(0.16 0.008 260) — card/panel
bg-auth-elevated  → oklch(0.20 0.008 260) — input / dropdown / raised element
border-auth-border → oklch(0.28 0.006 260) — all borders
```

### Text Hierarchy

```
text-auth-text    → oklch(0.98 0 0)       — primary / headings
text-auth-text-2  → oklch(0.70 0.01 260)  — secondary / descriptions
text-auth-text-3  → oklch(0.48 0.01 260)  — muted / labels / placeholders
```

### Secondary Palette (use sparingly, for data viz only)

```
text-auth-purple / bg-auth-purple-dim   → Storage / roles
text-auth-orange / bg-auth-orange-dim   → Limits / warnings context  
text-auth-cyan / bg-auth-cyan-dim       → Processing / real-time states
text-auth-error / bg-auth-error-dim     → Errors
```

