## 3. Never Do This ❌

```tsx
// ❌ WRONG — plain Tailwind blue/indigo
className="bg-blue-500 text-indigo-400 border-purple-500"

// ❌ WRONG — light backgrounds
className="bg-white text-gray-900"

// ❌ WRONG — hardcoded hex/rgb colors
style={{ background: "#22c55e", color: "#fff" }}

// ❌ WRONG — using brand-* tokens directly in components (use auth-* tokens instead)
className="bg-brand-500 text-brand-400"

// ❌ WRONG — generic Tailwind emerald without glow/shadow
className="bg-emerald-500" // alone, without shadow/hover states
```

