## 5. Typography Rules

- **ALL Tailwind text sizing should prefer fluid classes**: `text-fluid-xs`, `text-fluid-sm`, `text-fluid-base`, `text-fluid-lg`, `text-fluid-xl`, `text-fluid-2xl`
- **Section headings**: `text-sm font-bold tracking-tight uppercase text-auth-text-3`
- **Card subtitles**: `text-xs text-auth-text-2`
- **Labels**: `text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-auth-text-3`
- **Accent gradient text** (brand name): `bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent`

### Brand Name Rendering

```tsx
// ✅ Always render brand name like this:
Pulse<span className="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Knowledge</span>
```

---

## 6. Animation & Motion Rules

- **Hover lift**: use `.hover-lift` utility class (defined in globals.css)
- **Fade in**: use `animate-fade-in` (defined in globals.css)  
- **Button active**: always add `active:scale-[0.98]` for tactile feedback
- **Transitions**: always `transition-all` or `transition-colors` — never omit
- **Glow on hover for CTAs**: `hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(52,211,153,0.35)]`
- **Spinning loader**: always `<Loader2 className="animate-spin text-auth-accent" />`

---

## 7. Page Structure

Every page **must** use this background:

```tsx
<div className="min-h-screen bg-auth-bg text-auth-text relative overflow-hidden">
  {/* Optional: ambient glow effect */}
  <div className="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-[500px] w-[800px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/3 blur-[120px]"
    style={{ background: "radial-gradient(ellipse, oklch(0.75 0.19 160 / 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%)" }}
    aria-hidden="true" />
  ...
</div>
```

---

## 8. Layout Rules

- **Container**: always use `.container-responsive` (defined in globals.css, responsive max-widths)
- **Section gaps**: `py-8 flex flex-col gap-6` inside main
- **Grid**: prefer `grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4` for stats; `lg:grid-cols-3` for panels
- **Header**: `sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-white/[0.06] bg-auth-bg/75 backdrop-blur-2xl h-16`

---

## 9. Error States

### Full-Screen (auth failures only)
```tsx
<div className="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-auth-bg">
  <div className="w-full max-w-md bg-auth-surface border border-auth-border rounded-2xl p-6 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div className="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px] bg-auth-error" />
    ...
  </div>
</div>
```

### Non-Blocking Warning Banner
```tsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/20 bg-amber-950/20 px-4 py-3 text-xs text-amber-300">
  <AlertTriangle className="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-amber-400" />
  <span className="flex-1">{message}</span>
</div>
```

---

## 10. API Integration Pattern

- Server Actions in `src/app/actions/*.ts` — always `"use server"` at top
- `authClient.get/post/put/delete()` for authenticated endpoints
- Response envelope: `{ status: "1"|"0", error_code, msg, data }`
- Always handle `status === "0"` before using `data`
- Auth errors (`UNAUTHORIZED`) → `clearAuth()` + `router.push("/login")`
- Non-auth errors → graceful degradation (show empty state + warning banner)

---

## 11. File Conventions

```
src/app/(auth)/           → Auth pages (login, register, forgot-password)
src/app/actions/          → Server Actions (dashboard.ts, auth.ts, onboarding.ts)
src/components/auth/      → Auth UI components
src/components/dashboard/ → Dashboard components
src/components/onboarding/→ Onboarding wizard
src/types/                → TypeScript types
src/lib/                  → Utilities (auth-api.ts, authenticated-client.ts, token-storage.ts)
src/contexts/             → React contexts (auth-context.tsx)
src/hooks/                → Custom hooks (use-auth.ts)
```

